{"id":125287,"type":1,"name":"AZUMI","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/06/da/125287_8kSNM.jpg","summary":"時は幕末。桜田門外の変で大老・井伊直弼を人ごみに紛れて1人の刺客が討ち取った。凄腕の刺客「あずみ」である。次第に世の中が荒れてくる中、貧しいながらも穏やかに暮らしてる家族がいた。その家族の長男の名は向駿介。彼こそ、幼い頃に向家に養子に出されたあずみの双子の兄である。駿介と出会い、刺客として人を殺めることばかりを考えて生きてきたあずみは、彼の家族と交わっていくことで生き甲斐というものを見出していく。","info":"<li><span>册数: </span>18</li><li><span>话数: </span>125</li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/6749\">小学館</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/8262\">ビッグコミックスペリオール</a></li><li><span>作者: </span>小山ゆう</li><li><span>连载开始: </span>2009-01-09（2009年2号）</li><li><span>连载结束: </span>2014-02-28（2014年6号）</li>","collection":{"wish":2,"collect":1},"tags":[{"name":"漫画系列","count":2}],"staff":[{"id":6749,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2c/ec/6749_prsn_O9b2I.jpg","name":"小学馆","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8262,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/ec/a9/8262_prsn_NMvvK.jpg","name":"ビッグコミックスペリオール","desc":"连载杂志"}],"relations":[{"id":73205,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/88/e3/73205_KbzE7.jpg","title":"あずみ","type":"前传","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/73205"}],"comic":[{"id":125288,"name":"AZUMI-あずみ- 1","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/1b/8b/125288_jp.jpg"},{"id":125289,"name":"AZUMI-あずみ- 2","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/c3/cf/125289_jp.jpg"},{"id":125290,"name":"AZUMI-あずみ- 3","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/08/a5/125290_jp.jpg"},{"id":125291,"name":"AZUMI-あずみ- 4","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/44/a2/125291_jp.jpg"},{"id":125292,"name":"AZUMI-あずみ- 5","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/3a/28/125292_jp.jpg"},{"id":125293,"name":"AZUMI-あずみ- 6","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/d3/f4/125293_jp.jpg"},{"id":125294,"name":"AZUMI-あずみ- 7","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/9e/8a/125294_jp.jpg"},{"id":125295,"name":"AZUMI-あずみ- 8","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/58/63/125295_jp.jpg"},{"id":125296,"name":"AZUMI-あずみ- 9","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/2d/e0/125296_jp.jpg"},{"id":125297,"name":"AZUMI-あずみ- 10","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/49/7d/125297_jp.jpg"},{"id"